healing, continuing

00:39:31.220 --> 00:39:32.270 align:middle line:90%
giving people readings.

00:39:32.270 --> 00:39:33.390 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You love
helping people.

00:39:33.390 --> 00:39:34.340 align:middle line:84%
>>MARTENSON: I love
helping people.

00:39:34.340 --> 00:39:35.150 align:middle line:90%
I do.

