You know, they wanted to know.

00:39:58.150 --> 00:39:58.870 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Help me.

00:39:58.870 --> 00:39:59.380 align:middle line:90%
Help me.

00:39:59.380 --> 00:40:00.180 align:middle line:90%
>>MARTENSON: Yeah.

